#. <html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta content="Pali text from the Mahāsaṅgīti Tipiṭaka Buddhavasse 2500" name="description"><title></title></head><body><div id="text" lang="pli"><section class="sutta" id="pli-tv-bu-vb-np22"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np22:pts-cs0.1"
